><head><title>gluQuadricOrientation</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" type="text/css"/><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.59.1"/><link rel="home" href="index.xml" title="PyOpenGL 2.0.1.09 Man Pages"/><link rel="up" href="reference-GLU.xml" title="GLU"/><link rel="previous" href="gluQuadricNormals.3G.xml" title="gluQuadricNormals"/><link rel="next" href="gluQuadricTexture.3G.xml" title="gluQuadricTexture"/></head><body bgcolor="white" text="black" link="#0000FF" vlink="#840084" alink="#0000FF"><div class="navheader"><table width="100%" summary="Navigation header"><tr><th colspan="3" align="center">gluQuadricOrientation</th></tr><tr><td width="20%" align="left"><a accesskey="p" href="gluQuadricNormals.3G.xml">Prev</a> </td><th width="60%" align="center">GLU</th><td width="20%" align="right"> <a accesskey="n" href="gluQuadricTexture.3G.xml">Next</a></td></tr></table><hr/></div><div class="refentry" lang="en"><a name="gluQuadricOrientation.3G"/><div class="titlepage"/><div class="refnamediv"><a name="gluQuadricOrientation.3G-name"/><h2>Name</h2><p>gluQuadricOrientation &#8212; specify inside/outside orientation for quadrics</p></div><div class="refsynopsisdiv"><a name="gluQuadricOrientation.3G-c_spec"/><h2>C Specification</h2><table class="funcprototype" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td valign="top"><code>void <tt>gluQuadricOrientation</tt></code></td><td valign="top"><code>(</code></td><td valign="top"><code>GLUquadric* <i><tt>quad</tt></i>, GLenum <i><tt>orientation</tt></i>);</code></td></tr></table></div><div class="refsynopsisdiv"><a name="gluQuadricOrientation.3G-python_spec"/><h2>Python Specification</h2><table class="funcprototype" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td valign="top"><code><tt>gluQuadricOrientation</tt></code></td><td valign="top"><code>(</code></td><td valign="top"><code><i><tt>quad</tt></i>, <i><tt>orientation</tt></i>) &#8594; <tt>None</tt></code></td></tr></table></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en"><a name="gluQuadricOrientation.3G-parameters"/><h2>Parameters</h2><div class="variablelist"><dl><dt><span class="term"><i><tt>quad</tt></i></span></dt><dd>
						Specifies the quadrics object (created with <a href="gluNewQuadric.3G.xml"><tt>gluNewQuadric</tt></a>).
					</dd><dt><span class="term"><i><tt>orientation</tt></i></span></dt><dd>
						Specifies the desired orientation. Valid values are <tt>GLU_OUTSIDE</tt> and
						<tt>GLU_INSIDE</tt>.
					</dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en"><a name="gluQuadricOrientation.3G-description"/><h2>Description</h2><p>
			<tt>gluQuadricOrientation</tt> specifies what kind of orientation is desired for quadrics rendered with
			<i><tt>quad</tt></i>. The <i><tt>orientation</tt></i> values are as follows:
		</p><div class="variablelist"><dl><dt><span class="term"><tt>GLU_OUTSIDE</tt></span></dt><dd>
						Quadrics are drawn with normals pointing outward (the initial value).
					</dd><dt><span class="term"><tt>GLU_INSIDE</tt></span></dt><dd>
						Quadrics are drawn with normals pointing inward.
					</dd></dl></div><p>
			Note that the interpretation of <i><tt>outward</tt></i> and <i><tt>inward</tt></i> depends on the quadric
			being drawn.
		</p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en"><a name="gluQuadricOrientation.3G-see_also"/><h2>See Also</h2><p>
